      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In late 2016, former U.K. Prime Minister David Cameron spoke as part of the Blackstone Real Estate Global Limited Partners Conference at a dinner reception hosted at the American Museum of Natural History. Cameron was paid $120,000 for his time, according to a ",
